{{define "content"}}
<div class="bg-white px-6 py-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-600">
            Documentation
        </p>

        <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Getting Started
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8">
            OttoMap is a tool for TribeNet players to visualize their TribeNet maps.
            It reads your TribeNet turn reports and generates a Worldographer map that you can view on your
            computer.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
            <p class="mt-8">
                You should have received an email or DM with your account information and a link to your login page.
                You will need both to get started.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-8">
                Open the link in your login page in your browser.
                You should see the login screen with your account name filled in.
            </p>
            <figure class="mt-16">
                <img class="aspect-video rounded-xl bg-gray-50 object-cover" style="border: #6366f1 1px solid;"
                     src="/img/login-page.png"
                     alt="login page example">
                <figcaption class="mt-4 flex gap-x-2 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-500">
                    <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-gray-300" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                         aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                              d="M18 10a8 8 0 1 1-16 0 8 8 0 0 1 16 0Zm-7-4a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0ZM9 9a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h.253a.25.25 0 0 1 .244.304l-.459 2.066A1.75 1.75 0 0 0 10.747 15H11a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5h-.253a.25.25 0 0 1-.244-.304l.459-2.066A1.75 1.75 0 0 0 9.253 9H9Z"
                              clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    Login page for Clan 0987
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p class="mt-8">
                Note: the "@ottomap" in your account name is required;
                it tells the web server that you are authenticating with OttoMap.
                (In the future, this will be configurable.)
            </p>
            <p class="mt-8">
                Enter your password and click the "Sign in" button.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-8">
                You should now be logged in and viewing your dashboard.
                If not, please contact me on the Discord server.
            </p>
            <figure class="mt-16">
                <img class="aspect-video rounded-xl bg-gray-50 object-cover" style="border: #6366f1 1px solid;"
                     src="/img/dashboard-empty-page.png"
                     alt="initial dashboard page">
                <figcaption class="mt-4 flex gap-x-2 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-500">
                    <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-gray-300" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                         aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                              d="M18 10a8 8 0 1 1-16 0 8 8 0 0 1 16 0Zm-7-4a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0ZM9 9a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h.253a.25.25 0 0 1 .244.304l-.459 2.066A1.75 1.75 0 0 0 10.747 15H11a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5h-.253a.25.25 0 0 1-.244-.304l.459-2.066A1.75 1.75 0 0 0 9.253 9H9Z"
                              clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    Initial Dashboard for Clan 0987
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p class="mt-8">
                You can bookmark this page for easy access.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-8">
                You're now ready to upload your turn reports.
                If you've already saved your turn reports to a file, you can click the "Add reports" button to upload them.
                If you haven't, already, please review the steps in the
                <a href="/docs/converting-turn-reports" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">
                    Converting Turn Reports
                </a>
                document.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-8">
                For information on the Dashboard page, please see the
                <a href="/docs/dashboard-overview" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">
                    Dashboard overview
                </a>
                page.
            </p>
            <h2 class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
                Logging out
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6">
                OttoMap uses a cookie to remember your login, so you will not need to login again until your session expires, which is 2 weeks.
                You can logout at any time by navigating to the
                <a href="/logout" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">
                    Logout
                </a>
                page.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{{end}}
